title: Grape By Killer Fruits Vapetasia
description: Due to its exceptional flavor, this mix is ideal for ardent grape flavor lovers and guaranteed to increase levels of enjoyment. Killer Fruits Grape by Vapetasia is a fantastic new flavor that has been added to the well-known Killer Fruits collection. It features a blend of candy grape flavor and ripe grape flavor, creating a wonderfully delicious vape that you'll enjoy with each puff.
